  "index.problem.title": "Play More. Organize Less.",
  "index.problem.intro": "TournaQ makes beach volleyball events effortless.",
  "index.problem.body": "Create teams in seconds, launch social scramble formats, track every rally with a beautiful live scoreboard, and keep players focused on what matters most: playing volleyball and having fun.",
  "index.problem.nopaper": "No paper score sheets. No spreadsheets. No confusion.",
  "index.problem.text": "From casual beach sessions to competitive tournaments, TournaQ helps players, organizers, and clubs create better volleyball experiences with less effort and more excitement.",
  "index.problem.future": "The future of beach volleyball game & tournament management starts here.",
  "index.vision.title": "Where We're Headed",
