  "modes.swiss-system.construction": "Page Under Construction <span>This page is being updated. Content may be incomplete.</span>",
  "modes.swiss-system.intro": "The Swiss system runs a fixed number of rounds without elimination. After each round, teams are re-paired based on their current record — teams with similar win-loss records play each other. The final standings are determined by overall record after all rounds are complete. TournaQ generates pairings automatically each round and updates standings in real time.",
