  "modes.doghouse.hero.title": "Doghouse",
  "modes.doghouse.hero.subtitle": "Handle the pressure. Try to get out of the doghouse.",
  "modes.doghouse.status": "Available",
  "modes.doghouse.construction": "Page Under Construction <span>This page is being updated. Content may be incomplete.</span>",
  "modes.doghouse.intro": "Doghouse is a continuous play format for groups where not everyone can be on court at the same time. The losing team steps off and joins the back of a waiting queue — the \"doghouse\". The next team in the queue steps straight on to face the winners. Play never stops, and teams rotate through the queue until time runs out or a target win count is reached.",
